---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="panel section">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">这个站点怎么来的</h1>
    <p class="hero-copy">
      笔记原本写在私有 Obsidian 知识库中。发布时，脚本会抽取允许公开的笔记，
      处理内部链接和附件，再把结果送进 Astro 站点构建成静态网页。
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
